window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"The Book Case\" is a story that features Nelson DeMille's most famous (and successful) character, Detective John Corey, who has appeared in six DeMille novels: <i>Plum Island, The Lion's Game, Night Fall, Wild Fire,</i> and <i>The Lion</i>. In this story, we see John Corey in his early years as an NYPD Detective, before he became involved with the Federal Anti-Terrorist Task Force. </p>"; 
